sentences: Luther Nicholson (born July 6, 1989), better known by his stage name Lute, is an American rapper.
He released his first mixtape, West1996, on February 22, 2012.
His debut album, West1996 pt. 2, was released on September 29, 2017.
His second album, Gold Mouf, was released on October 4, 2021.
